snippet.title: The Legend of Silkroad (Arcade) Playthrough longplay retro video game
snippet.description: The Legend of Silkroad is a 2D side-scrolling beat 'em-up game that puts players in the shoes of either the heroes Munmoo from Korea, Sochun from China or Jamuka from Mongolia. The adventure leads you along the Silkroad, with a total of twenty-five different enemies.
